# Analytics Package

## Overview

The `analytics` package provides a wrapper around OpenPanel for logging events on both the client and server sides.

## File Structure

```
packages/analytics/
├── src/
│   ├── client.tsx     # Client-side analytics provider and track function
│   ├── events.ts      # Definitions for all trackable log events
│   ├── index.ts       # Main package exports
│   └── server.ts      # Server-side analytics setup and track function
├── package.json
└── tsconfig.json
```
